Center: Centre for Photonuclear Experiments Data, Moscow State University, Russia
ref: Jour: Yadernaya Fizika, Vol.58, Issue.5, p.773 (1995)
title: N-14(g,pn)C-12 Reaction up to Meson Production Threshold.

x4freetext: N-14(g,pn)C-12 Reaction up to Meson Production
Threshold.

x4codes.shortRef: Jour: Yadernaya Fizika, Vol.58, Issue.5, p.773 (1995)
Jour: Physics of Atomic Nuclei, Vol.58, Issue.5, p.712 (1995)

x4freetext: 15 % mixture of natural nitrogen with hydrogen at
atmosphere pressure.
Diffusion chamber in magnetic field.
Diffusion chamber.
Statistical errors are given.
The total cross section  and  angular distributions in
six energy  intervals  of the N-14(g,pn)C-12 reaction
have been measured by means of the diffusion  chamber
in magnetic field exposed to the bremsstrahlung g-ray
beam with energy up  to  150  MeV.  the  results  are
compared  with  the  predictions  of  the  correlated
pn-pair photon  absorption  model  in  the  range  of
energy over the giant resonance region.
Corrected by  V.Varlamov:  Datas  (two  to
four  digits) including that in reference and history
and reaction codes (DA,RSD,BRS,EXP to DA,,RSD/BRS,EXP
for SUBENTs 020 - 028) were changed.
REFERENCE    corrected   at   MSU   CDFE,
lowercase, DATA-CM in SUBENTs 002-028, ERR-S
Directly measurement of product angular distributions.
data  were  prepared  at the MSU INP CDFE  by
V.V.Varlamov.
